<title type="html"><![CDATA[Better fading]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5165&amp;p=47349#p47349"><![CDATA[
I considered using the emphasis bits, like I mentioned before, but gave up on the idea for a number of reasons.<br /><br />I ended up solving my problem by reordering the palette so that it's more friendly to hue and brightness transformations. The conversion table ended up a bit larger than I first wanted, but it will have to do for now. I'm tweaking the fading to be as smooth as possible.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Thu May 28, 2009 7:23 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
